<h1>To Create Environmental Audit Report</h1>
<ol>
<li>Choose the Create Environmental Audit Report option. <br>
A report is generated containing a table of Sample records with all parameter values <br>
grouped by Water Body and Sampler, sorted by date.</li>
<li>Select the Water Body and select parameters analysed at that body. <br>
A graph will be shown with these parameter and a horizontal line representing the <br>
exceedances applicable to each parameter.</li>
<li>Select an exceedance line and information about that exceedance will be displayed <br>
(which parameter it applies to its value.) Where a detection limit has been recorded, <br>
rather than an actual value, this will be highlighted on the report.</li>
</ol>
